<pc>」</pc>乃以弟澄為荊州都督<pc>，</pc>族弟敦為<placeName>青州</placeName>
<term>刺史</term>
<pc>，</pc>語之曰<pc>：</pc>
<pc>「</pc>
<quote>荊州有江<pc>、</pc>漢之固<pc>，</pc>
<placeName>青州</placeName>有負海之險<pc>，</pc>卿<measure quantity="2" unit="people">
<num value="2">二</num>人</measure>在外而吾居中<pc>，</pc>足以為<num value="3">三</num>窟矣<pc>。</pc>
