<pc>、</pc>
</placeName>青<placeName>徐</placeName>
<measure quantity="2" unit="prefectures">
<num value="2">二</num>州</measure>牧<pc>、</pc>都督緣海諸軍事<pc>，</pc>封東萊公<pc>；</pc>以靈為平北將軍<pc>。</pc>
