<measure quantity="4" unit="prefectures">
<num value="4">四</num>州</measure>
<pc>，</pc>所過攻陷郡縣<pc>，</pc>多殺守令<pc>，</pc>有眾數<num value="10000">萬</num>
<pc>；</pc>苟晞與之連戰<pc>，</pc>不能克<pc>。</pc>夏<pc>，</pc>
<measure quantity="4" unit="months">
